Author: antediluvian5
Text: There’s nothing wrong with having normal preferences, yes. But the way I feel about other people’s bodies is literally causing daily distress and guilt in my life. There’s a difference between just not being attracted to bigger people versus feeling repulsed.

Author: ErikaaSky3
Text: Even people without EDs tend to prefer their parents a certain size. I don’t think it’s necessarily a bad thing
